wdi2-SP.DYN.IMRT.MA.IN.def: Infant mortality rate, male is the number of male infants dying before reaching one year of age, per 1,000 male live births in a given year.
wdi2-SP.DYN.IMRT.MA.IN.name: Mortality rate, infant
wdi2-SP.DYN.IMRT.MA.IN.source: Estimates developed by the UN Inter-agency Group for Child Mortality Estimation (UNICEF, WHO, World Bank, UN DESA Population Division) at www.childmortality.org.
